XPW                                         Robert Duncan, November 1990

Prolog interface to the Poplog Widget Set (Xpw) developed by Andreas
Schoter at the University of Sussex.

Files in this directory:

    xpw.pl
        Initialisation file.

    help/
    teach/
        Introductory documentation.

    demo/
        A demonstration program.

    lib/
        Library code.

    ref/
        Reference information on predicates and resources.


Reconsulting the file "xpw.pl" initialises search lists so that the
documentation and library files become automatically available.

To find out more, do:

    ?- [-'$popcontrib/x/prolog/xpw/xpw.pl'].
    ?- teach xprolog
